{
  "stem": "13141.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said to me, that she thinks that my mother must have died at the beginning of December because she was practically starved to death.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The rest of my family, I found out, not from, from people, but from records because a few years ago, my brother Larry, and my wife Laura, and my sister-in-law, we went to Poland on an organized trip.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went also to Theresienstadt, to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We took a car to Stutthof because the group didn't go to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a Saturday-- it was a Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the group was free to do whatever they wanted to do because some, maybe, wanted to go to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we talked it over Friday night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I already said, let's take a car, let's rent a car, and let's go to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From Warsaw to go to Stutthof is about, I would say, maybe three or three and a half hours, one way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Stutthof is at the Baltic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's near what they call, today, Gdansk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At the time, it was called Danzig.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's also very close of where the-- where they-- where they tried on the life of Hitler in June of 1944-- just about 15 or 20 miles from there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The guide, in fact, asked us whether we wanted to stop by there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But frankly, we, we wanted to go to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We went to Stuffhof, and we wanted to go-- come back again the same day because there were no hotels at the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was still communist, you know-- Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we went to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was, of course, a terrible sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's a museum now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's-- they built it up again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They, they painted it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
